&quot;Why don't you become a maid of my Akabane family?&quot; 

Amako appeared in front of Hinako, a beautician apprentice who lives in extreme poverty. 

&quot;If you go along with favorable conditions, you will find 'Chicken Village', an object of worship.&quot; 

Hinako, who is confused by the strangely beautiful closed world with special customs such as polygamy, was entrusted with the care of the hair of the village head, Kay. Beautiful Kay with his long shining, hair. 

Only his wife can hear Kay's precious voice, but that night, I heard a lustrous voice from inside the room.
